id: pm-8rjn
title: Wire pm init approval flow and declined guidance persistence
description: "Extend pm init so missing AGENTS/CLAUDE guidance is surfaced safely: prompt in TTY, persist declines in project settings, and allow a later explicit init option to add guidance."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[5]: agent-ux,bootstrap,init,pm-cli,settings
created_at: "2026-05-17T08:59:31.342Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-17T10:09:42.936Z"
author: codex-agent
acceptance_criteria: pm init asks once in interactive mode when guidance is missing; yes writes guidance; no records project-level decline; future default init runs do not ask after decline; pm init --agent-guidance add writes guidance even after decline; non-interactive init never waits for input; result payload includes deterministic guidance status for JSON/TOON output.
